CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1784530074
OL,3,CE-scooters travelling close to the
OL,4,Cback of a bus could have ended 'in
OL,5,Ctragedy'
OL,7,FA bus company is urging people to
OL,8,Funderstand the dangers of using e-
OL,9,Fscooters on public roads after CCTV
OL,10,Fcaptured two riders travelling
OL,11,Fdirectly behind one of its buses.
OL,13,FBorders Buses says the footage,
OL,14,Fcapture in Burnfoot in Hawick, shows
OL,15,Fhow little room they have to react if
OL,16,Fa bus needs to brake suddenly, which
OL,17,Fcould put the riders, passenger and
OL,18,Fdriver at serious risk.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
