PN,32802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1784530074
OL,3,CE-scooters travelling close to the
OL,4,Cback of a bus could have ended 'in
OL,5,Ctragedy'
OL,7,FThe operator is asking parents to
OL,8,Fspeak to their children around staying
OL,9,Fsafe on e-scooters.
OL,11,FLee Young, from the company, said:
OL,12,F"Watching the CCTV footage, it's clear
OL,13,Fhow quickly this situation could have
OL,14,Fturned into a tragedy.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,329,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1784530074
OL,3,CE-scooters travelling close to the
OL,4,Cback of a bus could have ended 'in
OL,5,Ctragedy'
OL,7,F"A bus can weigh many tonnes and, if
OL,8,Fit needs to brake suddenly, anyone
OL,9,Ftravelling directly behind it has very
OL,10,Flittle chance of avoiding a collision.
OL,11,FWe want this footage to act as a
OL,12,Freminder that these decisions have
OL,13,Freal consequences."
OL,15,FBorders Buses operates CCTV across its
OL,16,Ffleet to help protect passengers,
OL,17,Fdrivers and the wider community.
OL,18,FFootage is regularly used to support
OL,19,Finvestigations into dangerous or anti-
OL,20,Fsocial behaviour.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
