PN,32804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1784530074
OL,3,CE-scooters travelling close to the
OL,4,Cback of a bus could have ended 'in
OL,5,Ctragedy'
OL,7,FIt's a matter that Police Scotland are
OL,8,Falso involved in, with Hawick
OL,9,FCommunity Policing Team raising
OL,10,Fconcern over the use of the scooters
OL,11,Fin and around Hawick.
OL,13,FAlthough they can be purchased, E-
OL,14,Fscooters cannot be used legally on
OL,15,Fpublic roads, pavements, cycle paths,
OL,16,For other public areas in Scotland.
OL,18,FWhere can you ride an E-scooter
OL,19,Flegally?
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
