PN,32805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1784530074
OL,3,CE-scooters travelling close to the
OL,4,Cback of a bus could have ended 'in
OL,5,Ctragedy'
OL,7,FA Hawick Community Policing Team
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "Local officers
OL,9,Fhave received increasing reports and
OL,10,Fconcerns regarding the use of E-
OL,11,FScooters in and around Hawick.
OL,13,F"We would ask parents speak with their
OL,14,Fchild about the legal restrictions
OL,15,Fsurrounding E-Scooters and the
OL,16,Fpotential consequences of using them
OL,17,Fin public places.
OL,26,@pD@TOUuD@AOU
