PN,32806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F328A1784530074
OL,3,CE-scooters travelling close to the
OL,4,Cback of a bus could have ended 'in
OL,5,Ctragedy'
OL,7,F"If your child owns an E-Scooter, you
OL,8,Fmay wish to consider removing access
OL,9,Fto it or disposing of it appropriately
OL,10,Fbefore action is taken.
OL,12,F"We appreciate your support in helping
OL,13,Fto keep our young people and the wider
OL,14,Fcommunity safe."
